---
title: Roasted Zucchini & Onion Torta with Guacamole & Roasted Potato Wedges
description: Looking for a dynamic dinner? Meet the torta! Our take on this classic Mexican sandwich starts with crusty bread slathered with savory, spiced mashed beans and a layer of guac, then stacked high with roasted onion, sautéed zucchini, fresh tomato, Monterey Jack, and pickled jalapeño. With roasted potato wedges on the side, this super-stuffed sammie turns torta-lly dinner worthy!
